<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Three66 Espresso Bar | Lilli Pilli</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@700;800;900&family=Raleway:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --fox-teal: #00b8b8; /* Signature Fox & Bow Teal */
            --fox-dark: #222222;
            --fox-light: #ffffff;
            --fox-gray: #f4f4f4;
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
            color: var(--fox-dark);
            background-color: var(--fox-light);
        }

        h1, h2, h3, .nav-links a {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        /* --- Fox & Bow Sidebar Style Nav (Desktop) --- */
        nav {
            padding: 30px 5%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            background: var(--fox-light);
            border-bottom: 4px solid var(--fox-teal);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .logo { 
            font-weight: 900; 
            font-size: 28px; 
            color: var(--fox-dark);
            border: 3px solid var(--fox-dark);
            padding: 5px 15px;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--fox-dark);
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-left: 25px;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--fox-teal); }

        /* --- Full Screen Hero --- */
        .hero {
            height: 90vh;
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.3)), url('view.JPG') center/cover no-repeat;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .hero-content h1 {
            font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem);
            line-height: 0.9;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .hero-content p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto 30px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* --- The Famous "Action Buttons" --- */
        .action-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            background: var(--fox-dark);
        }

        .action-btn {
            padding: 50px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border: 1px solid #333;
            transition: background 0.3s;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .action-btn:hover { background: var(--fox-teal); }
        .action-btn span { font-family: 'Montserrat'; font-weight: 800; font-size: 18px; text-transform: uppercase; }

        /* --- Content Sections --- */
        .section { padding: 80px 10%; }
        .section-title {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .section-title::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 10px;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 15px;
            background: var(--fox-teal);
            z-index: -1;
            opacity: 0.5;
        }

        .about-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 50px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .about-text p { margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; }

        /* --- Menu / Food Section --- */
        .menu-preview { background: var(--fox-gray); }
        
        .food-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .food-item {
            background: white;
            border: 5px solid var(--fox-dark);
            padding: 30px;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }

        .food-item:hover { transform: rotate(-1deg) scale(1.02); }
        .food-item h3 { color: var(--fox-teal); margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 1.4rem; }

        /* --- Footer (Fox Style) --- */
        footer {
            background: var(--fox-dark);
            color: white;
            padding: 80px 10% 40px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 40px;
        }

        .footer-col h4 {
            color: var(--fox-teal);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .footer-col p { margin-bottom: 10px; opacity: 0.8; }

        .social-icons { margin-top: 20px; font-size: 24px; }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .section-title { font-size: 2rem; }
            nav { flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; }
            .nav-links a { margin: 0 10px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <div class="logo">THREE66</div>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="#about">The Vibe</a>
            <a href="#menu">Menu</a>
            <a href="#contact">Find Us</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>COASTAL<br><span style="color: var(--fox-teal);">VIBES.</span></h1>
            <p>Specialty coffee and killer food served right on Mosquito Bay.</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="action-grid">
        <a href="https://three66.mobi-order.com/" class="action-btn">
            <span>Order Pickup</span>
        </a>
        <a href="#menu" class="action-btn">
            <span>View Menu</span>
        </a>
        <a href="#about" class="action-btn">
            <span>The Vibe</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/three66espresso" class="action-btn">
            <span>Instagram</span>
        </a>
    </section>

    <section id="about" class="section">
        <div class="about-grid">
            <div class="about-text">
                <h2 class="section-title">A Hidden Gem</h2>
                <p>At Three66, we blend premium café culture with the relaxed beauty of the coast. We proudly serve specialty <strong>ONA Coffee</strong>, ensuring every cup is poured to absolute perfection.</p>
                <p>Whether you’re in for a 5 AM caffeine hit or a leisurely lunch on the deck, we’ve got you. We're pet friendly, fully licensed, and full of plants.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="about-image">
                <img src="store-front.JPG" alt="Three66" style="width: 100%; border: 10px solid var(--fox-dark);">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="menu" class="section menu-preview">
        <h2 class="section-title">Feed the Soul</h2>
        <div class="food-grid">
            <div class="food-item">
                <h3>The Best Beef Burger</h3>
                <p>A local favorite. Premium beef, fresh ingredients, and flavours that pack a punch.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="food-item">
                <h3>Classic Eggs Benny</h3>
                <p>Served with fresh salmon and roasted cherry tomatoes. The ultimate weekend brunch.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="food-item">
                <h3>Sweet Corn Fritters</h3>
                <p>Crispy on the outside, fluffy inside served with choice of bacon, salmon or halloumi.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer id="contact">
        <div class="footer-col">
            <h4>Find Us</h4>
            <p>Shop 1 / 366 George Bass Dr</p>
            <p>Lilli Pilli, NSW 2536</p>
            <p><strong>(02) 4471 3947</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-col">
            <h4>Hours</h4>
            <p>WED - SUN: 5:00 AM - 2:00 PM</p>
            <p>Closed Mon/Tue</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-col">
            <h4>Follow Three66</h4>
            <p>Join the community on Instagram for daily specials and bay views.</p>
            <div class="social-icons">@three66espresso</div>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
